<paragraph blockId="11.[189,1398,1919,2028]" lastBlockId="12.[189,1398,267,364]" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="13" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
Cockerell considered describing 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1949" box="[573,696,1965,1992]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis box="[573,696,1965,1992]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">C. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
under the name “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1926" box="[903,1053,1965,1992]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="wilmattae">
<emphasis box="[903,1053,1965,1992]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">C. wilmattae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, as an homage to his second wife. However, this name had already been used by 
<bibRefCitation author="Cockerell" box="[811,1024,2001,2028]" firstAuthor="Cockerell" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="214 - 226" refId="ref20022" refString="Cockerell, T. D. A. 1926 a. XXVIII. - Descriptions and records of bees. - CVIII. Annals and Magazine of Natural History 17 (98): 214 - 226. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222932608633395" type="journal article" year="1926" yearSuffix="a">Cockerell (1926a)</bibRefCitation>
himself for a species described from 
<collectingRegion box="[255,367,267,293]" country="Peru" name="Arequipa" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Arequipa</collectingRegion>
, southern 
<collectingCountry box="[495,549,268,294]" name="Peru" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Peru</collectingCountry>
(see below). 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure" box="[718,885,267,294]" firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="114 - 123" refId="ref21409" refString="Moure J. S. 1969. Notas sobre algumas especies de Centris da Guiana (Hym., Apoidea). Anais da Academia brasileira de Ciencias 41 (1): 114 - 123." type="journal article" year="1969">Moure (1969)</bibRefCitation>
synonymized 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1949" box="[1064,1191,267,294]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis box="[1064,1191,267,294]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1899" box="[1265,1391,268,294]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inermis">
<emphasis box="[1265,1391,268,294]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. inermis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Snelling" box="[189,372,303,329]" firstAuthor="Snelling" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="1 - 69" refId="ref22174" refString="Snelling R. R. 1984. Studies on the taxonomy and distribution of American Centridine bees (Hymenoptera: Anthophoridae). Contributions in Science, Los Angeles County Museum of Natural History 347: 1 - 69." type="journal article" year="1984">Snelling (1984)</bibRefCitation>
newly proposed this synonymy, apparently ignoring Moure’s paper. Later, 
<bibRefCitation author="Roig-Alsina" firstAuthor="Roig-Alsina" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="171 - 193" refId="ref21814" refString="Roig-Alsina A. 2000. Claves para las especies argentinas de Centris (Hymenoptera, Apidae), con descripcion de nuevas especies y notas sobre distribucion. Revista del Museo argentino de Ciencias naturales (n. s.) 2 (2): 171 - 193." type="journal article" year="2000">Roig-Alsina (2000)</bibRefCitation>
cited 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1899" box="[339,461,338,364]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inermis">
<emphasis box="[339,461,338,364]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. inermis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Erichson" baseAuthorityYear="1848" box="[703,799,338,364]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="varia">
<emphasis box="[703,799,338,364]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. varia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
